    "media:imagetext": "AIR FRANCE's Concorde 001— Delta-winged\nConcorde 001, a product of Anglo-Franco joint\nprogram, has already made a successful test flight,\nmarking 1,900 kph, which is almost two times faster\nthan speed of sound. The inauguration of scheduled\nflights over the Atlantic is expected in 1973, then\nthe present flying hours between London and\nNew York will be reduced to 3 hours and 17 min:\nSeating capacity: 128 Cruising speed: 1,450 mph.\nMaximum range: 4,000 miles.\nPOST CARD\nAFFIX\nSTAMP\nHERE\n* *\n*\nAIR FRANCE\nChat, Rit, B$#1, 900kmiI \u003c EACARL to 1 it\n#1973¥¾407⅚ 77¾77½1#⅜77+\n95## #36.437 km.\n1 #14#3-00-7214\nB.S: 1)3555 : 3 B5 | 1755 1: 4: 3 ).\n010\nPUB. BY NEC NIPPON BEAUTY CARD CENTER INC\n©\n§ NBC'\n2015.166.0149",
